      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for some TLC and a fresh start! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a solid foundation for anyone looking to restore a classic or use it for parts. It's an affordable entry point for a dedicated hobbyist ready to bring a car back to its former glory!",
